        "author_role": "REVIEWER",
        "timestamp": "2018-02-01 03:12:23.000000000",
        "message": "Patch Set 1: Code-Review-1\n\nActually the change would be just to remove the comment - Mayank, to preserve functionality - why don't we just skip the prepull of the config container if your sh script work needs a major retrofit to handle the multiline image/tag.",
        "patchset_number": 1
      },
      {
        "id": "2919adc5050d8d37002be36de491d5dd607f5fff",
        "author": {
          "account_id": 2535,
          "name": "Mayank Gupta",
